{"tid":201834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鐘意一個唔鐘意自己既人?","createTime":"2017-04-15T05:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T15:12:33.000Z","uid":16181,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6552202a3354f8ec0d12c49e8f6c40472a9d2a76","tid":201834,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:19:36.000Z","msg":"雖然只係相處過兩個幾月，但果種感覺真係好難忘。<br />\n成日都會諗起佢，成日都會主動搵佢<br />\n其實我可以做既都已經做曬～已經好主動<br />\n暗示過、約過，見面果陣都有說有笑，但WHATSAPP就好冷淡<br />\n我都知自己根本無機會，就諗住放棄<br />\n直接同佢講我成日纏住佢係因為鐘意佢<br />\n佢都直接派左好人卡俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身都諗住過多排果種感覺就會淡，但原來係唔會<br />\n過左兩個月無再見過面，都仍然係咁掛住佢<br />\n我識過既女仔當中，得佢俾過呢種感覺我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲好記得佢曾經同我講過以下果番說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「其實將來D野邊話得埋喎！好似我同果個A好似好熟咁，都係因為佢同我好多共同興趣，共同經歷，又一齊番學。但遲D可能都會某D原因就唔再熟架喇。感情呢D野邊有得話永遠？」<br />\n我果時諗，其實感情呢樣野係有永遠<br />\n因為我覺得我永遠都會咁鐘意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打絲打都有個唔鐘意自己既人？到底幾耐先放得低？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11de202a6399267d976a6c533da385a7d65134b8","tid":201834,"uid":6170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"鍾意左三年"},{"pid":"425cf2482c6767c4589501c6796ce7a763952938","tid":201834,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意左三年</blockquote><br />\n由這一分鐘開始計起春風秋雨間<br />\n限我對你以半年時間慢慢的心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0969199ee621555d268d281386007fe8acb6549","tid":201834,"uid":72816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"有 被個衰人送左張好人卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb863bd18b1f2c929959a6bb8571a05abb74add","tid":201834,"uid":89969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:28:38.000Z","msg":"明明見面唔會咁 但係whatsapp就好冷淡 灰剔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d39a930c963c5e05a8e18148629409ce9e56c3","tid":201834,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 被個衰人送左張好人卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有冇掛住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無覺得自己唔夠好，人地情願單身都唔接受？"},{"pid":"b8ff5c49a984e4435473e7ed2697cb112b6a7bec","tid":201834,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"你以為永遠啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一年之後你仲係咁鐘意佢先好講啦"},{"pid":"44798d45f579fc1368cab94c55c57576ee7782a8","tid":201834,"uid":72816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:31:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有 被個衰人送左張好人卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有冇掛住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無覺得自己唔夠好，人地情願單身都唔接受？</blockquote><br />\n自己唔夠成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b02670435e7b1807e92409b5f44e4d7bb2b8ca","tid":201834,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"仆街 嗰陣佢同我講要去同人表白個表情 應該一世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f307336576de84bfbad5fcd10e3f3cef50f4652","tid":201834,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你以為永遠啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一年之後你仲係咁鐘意佢先好講啦</blockquote><br />\n其他女仔根本無俾到呢種感覺我<br />\n同佢一齊真係好舒服，佢都係咁同我講過<br />\n但最後我根本再約唔到佢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a875d28a2b0445d9847b2e831c4fa87dbf693c21","tid":201834,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆街 嗰陣佢同我講要去同人表白個表情 應該一世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但表白果個人唔係你"},{"pid":"fe956b6c660c384d8840292abd10fa1312561fe5","tid":201834,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仆街 嗰陣佢同我講要去同人表白個表情 應該一世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但表白果個人唔係你</blockquote><br />\n係啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ef139255633bd085cbd7f73f7c78b1992c600b","tid":201834,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仆街 嗰陣佢同我講要去同人表白個表情 應該一世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但表白果個人唔係你</blockquote><br />\n係啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你啱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050e926eca3c5e51998dd2dcba7684d53447c172","tid":201834,"uid":106130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:56:35.000Z","msg":"呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但已經放棄，講左大家都唔會再搵大家"},{"pid":"4112c47a2c194ba00afbb2c9d2f8b9d181bdb5d5","tid":201834,"uid":60861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"八年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf5b298ddfb990179bc9b16aaa9a9cde6cb3f43","tid":201834,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"我真係到而家都唔明 點解佢去同人表白要話比我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60caea8970210a70838303d705955859dcb4cb1f","tid":201834,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我真係到而家都唔明 點解佢去同人表白要話比我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為佢根本唔知你鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a666831082a713b08a9f02f567be1f18f1f55c49","tid":201834,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我真係到而家都唔明 點解佢去同人表白要話比我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為佢根本唔知你鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早知就應該無friend做 <br />\n好撚犯賤 有時反而會沾沾 起碼我係第一個知佢點同而家條仔一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 但知黎做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d879df29a64977b977ad4906b5921cfa343be8b7","tid":201834,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"痾完尿照下自己咩樣<br />\n打開銀包睇下入面有幾錢"},{"pid":"e9674f61f27ac656d272936623c0d6f130dc032b","tid":201834,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我真係到而家都唔明 點解佢去同人表白要話比我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為佢根本唔知你鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早知就應該無friend做 <br />\n好撚犯賤 有時反而會沾沾 起碼我係第一個知佢點同而家條仔一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 但知黎做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望他是真的比我還要愛你～<br />\n我才會逼自己離開"},{"pid":"f3b809a73a383962cdc454bbf3b4d9db5a0a14a9","tid":201834,"uid":16743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eca180ce9e458e42848114fed5618034e267b9f","tid":201834,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我真係到而家都唔明 點解佢去同人表白要話比我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為佢根本唔知你鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早知就應該無friend做 <br />\n好撚犯賤 有時反而會沾沾 起碼我係第一個知佢點同而家條仔一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 但知黎做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望他是真的比我還要愛你～<br />\n我才會逼自己離開</blockquote><br />\n佢地拍左都幾年喇 好穩定嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家我鍾意佢嘅感覺已經淡到無乜<br />\n但係佢預備去表白嗰陣嘅對話 <br />\n聽住佢係咁講 同埋仲要正常答佢<br />\n個感受係到而家都仲係好深 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd65926446cb9639cce5c850b796a6dc2d5af320","tid":201834,"uid":48900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:48:29.000Z","msg":"比佢收埋做兵添<br />\n其實個幾個月佢都對我好好 成日都痴埋一齊<br />\n口講話係未想拍拖<br />\n但其實如果真係鍾意既話 一早一齊左啦<br />\n洗撚拖咁耐都話係未想拍拖咩<br />\n根本就係唔捨得有人對佢好<br />\n<br />\n個陣我身邊啲朋友屌過晒 想我醒<br />\n自己都係中個頭埋去 無計<br />\n後來發生左啲野 太絕望 <br />\n覺得真係將自己做到好cheap好賤既下把 <br />\n先決心抽身 <br />\n前前後後2、3個月 依家乜事都無<br />\n個陣以為會沉好耐 <br />\n點知最近知佢拍左拖 我都無乜野<br />\n<br />\n依家諗番轉頭 可能我都唔係好鍾意佢掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87091f47f9edfd8918c5c69c371e2d789dd4e085","tid":201834,"uid":6989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:52:52.000Z","msg":"明明見面唔會咁 但係whatsapp就好冷淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都唔冷淡, 肯覆既時候就好似見面咁, 有講有笑, 唔覆既時候就心掛掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdc60d2b6fbb648f2073debf15a8b77378e60ae","tid":201834,"uid":6989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明見面唔會咁 但係whatsapp就好冷淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都唔冷淡, 肯覆既時候就好似見面咁, 有講有笑, 唔覆既時候就心掛掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲同唔同佢講鐘意佢好呢,唔係表白果種, 純粹講出自己既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}